Title: I’m fucked up at 4am Friday. market is closed. I’m seeing animals in my charts
Should I start investing now?
Body: As an 18-year-old high school student, I have been researching investment options and have come across conflicting advice regarding which platform to use. After observing this page for some time, I have learned that Robinhood and Acorn may not be the best options, and that Fidelity or Think or Swim may be more suitable. I have not yet made any investments, as I am still conducting research. I would appreciate any advice on whether I should start investing and how to proceed. Thank you for your time.
